    Megatron stepped in between Rowdy Wolf and Kitkat. He held both his hands 
up and glared at them both. "Stop this at once! You are to use your hatred to 
defeat the Maximals, not on each other. Not that I wouldnt want to see a good 
fight, but I cant spare troops right now. Yes."

    Black Aracnia returned to Darkmouse and examined her hand. "Well, Liquid 
Energon is very powerful. You should be thankful, now you can heal without a 
CR chamber. Your very powerful. The shakes will go in time, and you shouldnt 
worry to much about them."
